{"tid":637942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國制裁香港在即，大家執生！","createTime":"2018-04-22T09:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T12:36:13.000Z","uid":53577,"like":222,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"7daf5c73565b758a45315d5f901b851a0bd66d51","tid":637942,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:29:21.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰美國係絕對唔會放過香港的！二十年來大陸靠香港人投資及輸入資金技術等等價值幾十萬億計！因為咁大陸先能夠發到咁大！(參考俄羅斯！冇香港=冇得搞)。<br />\n<br />\n咁美國會點樣封殺香港呢？<br />\n我相信美國會用精確打擊(但同時唔會容許大陸將港元改掛人民幣，因為會等於抛售美元，同令中共獲取百萬億資產)<br />\n<br />\n美國最先會連同盟友，重點針對賣港賊同中共外籍家屬，以反人類罪同洗黑錢罪搜捕佢哋，再扶助香港民主及本土派，抗衡同打擊中共。最後中共會喺冇選擇之下比香港獨立。"},{"pid":"2949d2234ea0d888029991715ad2076de43ecd98","tid":637942,"uid":118502,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace8c5dab8a4f3a7eeb43afcfd25c7827fb9e9f6","tid":637942,"uid":53577,"like":82,"dislike":2,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:31:39.000Z","msg":"撇除民族主義牌，港獨對中共最有利！"},{"pid":"1119a87f9f5c76a57708ba85cb2ea20fbf2f9d3a","tid":637942,"uid":6604,"like":78,"dislike":4,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:33:03.000Z","msg":"其實港元peg唔peg美金<br />\n美國無權話事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ec75ebd51716421f4f31a905510772cc6d2a16","tid":637942,"uid":53577,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:33:57.000Z","msg":"當中蝈比美國制到痴肺時候，中共只在乎重有冇得延續落去，情形就同70年代咁，有啖飯食已講聲多謝。"},{"pid":"30568919eaeed41410f03246b0f52d9acf74c368","tid":637942,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"1119a87f9f5c76a57708ba85cb2ea20fbf2f9d3a","tid":637942,"uid":6604,"like":78,"dislike":4,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:33:03.000Z","msg":"其實港元peg